      We have made it extremely easy to join our community. Simply fill out the form below to get signed up, we will NEVER ask you for ANY of your banking details. You will be able to login to this website at any time and join discussions, vote on important issues, and learn more about how to manage your finances as a dasher. We are not only here to help get you paid immediately, but we are also here to promote financial understanding. Meaning, we want to help you and each other strive for a better financial future. We have materials that will help you understand budgeting, saving, investing, and the responsible use of credit. It is important to state that we are not financial advisors, but we are here to help you learn everything you can to put yourself in control of your financial freedom!
    </p>
